Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:20.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,宇佐美学姐好狠毒!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然没有新的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但隔壁的储藏室里好像有个老的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁那是我们社团的储藏室吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我入社的时候  就已经基本不使用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,梦子老师或许不知道拿哪一把钥匙开门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就问问小山老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,…喂  你们干什么呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这门真是不太好开…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…就这点程度  根本不算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,分明喘得这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,进去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,空间大概是活动室的一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是灰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,窗户也不方便打开…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  日光灯也打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还是趁早赶紧找到它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,画得真好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  好好找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这漫画真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我小学时候读过的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了  找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就拜托你们关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得好紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看到没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你这副得意的表情是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这根本不算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,先别提这个  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是和内卷同处一室…你也可千万别因此失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}身不由己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,失控?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀…门一关就变热了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还是得通通风才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,…咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得紧也不至于…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,居然这么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是是  是我小看你了  对不起  行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该说你孱弱无力  骨瘦如柴  面色苍白!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不…你没说得这么严重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  既然要道歉  就得更加有诚意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  这箱子上写着「石膏像」三个字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊  宇佐美同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷  快来开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,比一开始卡得更紧了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,应该得怪你当时锤了一下门吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?  又成我的错了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我脸上沾了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好近!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呼…呼出的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,轻叩着我的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是可蕾特同学的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,学姐他们回去了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,让她把老师叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学  听得见吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这扇门打不开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,天色这么晚了  我也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  手机呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没戏  在包里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多要到放学时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷…如  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没有人注意到我们  该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,既然门打不开  也只得维持现状了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的情况就是在这里住一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(457.998,381.763)\frz248.5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs40\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(460.998,407.763)\frz250.7}··
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办  如果继续变冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别突然这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,才不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?  很暖和吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你从刚才开始就在说些什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,天已经黑透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么蹲在角落里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  怎么可能没感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在慌死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…在这又小又黑的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,直到明早  都得二人…独处…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,会起灰的  别打滚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学你没事吧  刚才就怪怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有事!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩得在这儿过一晚哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,都开始胡思乱想那种事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,社长说的那句话还怎么反驳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,内…内卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  我可是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给你看看我家甜心的厉害之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,摁下这个按钮  眼睛就会发光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  真亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这还是我第一次觉得内卷你的手办厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做的话  或许会让夜值巡逻的老师注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是又得好好巡逻才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊  梦子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  果然还是太黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那道光是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没人在才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,记得是这间来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才听到什么声音了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你也听到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是妖怪之类的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是以前社员的纪念照吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?  是照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  窗户这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,像不像是一张脸?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说过让你别吓唬我了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再这样我就把这个给折断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,比妖怪还可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你还来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吓唬你啦  你看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这里应该是这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是门吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,从位置上看  另一边就是活动室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷  你把那边的箱子移开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害  原来这里相连在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好可蕾特同学没有把门锁上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果就那样待了一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他们以后会怎么捉弄我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了石膏像了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我来搬石膏像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈打了好多通电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老师  您为何会在这种地方睡觉呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是现在还是以前都会有人对石膏像涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz278\pos(183.998,137.763)}贤弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz262\pos(614.998,193.763)}大哥哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz334\pos(183.998,204.763)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\pos(587.998,255.763)\frz336.9}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和短发波波头合起来就是…波啵午安!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧  很有趣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  这本漫画也好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  这本我也看过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这本很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,女主角有超能力的那一部对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,必杀技非常帅气  像这样…啪啪噼里啪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这间隐藏房间真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,既可以尽情看漫画又能够放松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你随时过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看起来聊得很高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做功课  所以可以请你们安静一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  功课在家里做不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们安静一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.07,Comment,,0,0,0,,你到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我不就不知道你们在做什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?  那当然是在看漫画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太安静的话总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喵喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什么夹在漫画里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,宝物的所在之处?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给未来的美术社员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}俺有一宝贝疙瘩  就藏在咱校园里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,吾有秘宝  藏于黉门之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}看你们能解开谜题  去挖出宝贝不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,望尔等窥破机关以继承秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(630,660)}希望俺这宝贝能找个好人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,若蒙菩萨心肠者得之  善哉善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害  是寻宝游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你要玩玩看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要玩  我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来刚好宇佐美同学就自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也能够方便她集中精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们赶快开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,到了休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在刚好是休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,暗号1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,「离开活动室并前往绅士的小屋」上面这么写
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,绅士的小屋是指哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是脑筋急转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,顺带一提暗号2是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「前往从绅士的小屋的窗户看得见的这个地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得至少是有窗户的房间才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此  是指男厕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,的确很「绅士」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这里就麻烦内卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为身为淑女的我们是不能进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  淑女?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是了个是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是了个是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,从窗户看得见的这的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一封奇怪的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也没什么特别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?  内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你看她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(555,660)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(685,660)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子想出来也不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候就是普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方  这个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(663,660)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是「这」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(760,660)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此  确实是这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好  内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉变得有趣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  下个提示是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,暗号3 「找出字母」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?  就这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,问题来了  登登
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里来看的话?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是U
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你真行  伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我脑筋急转弯淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个  暗号4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,「从找到的字母的末端开始  前进?步」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,「?步」?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,U的末端是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,步数是从1853到1890的向日葵的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道答案是什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  还不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,给一个提示  给一个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她很享受谜题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,提示  这是关于梵高的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(520,660)}Gogh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是什么来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.91,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}注：日语中「梵高」和「五步」的发音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,1步  2步  3步  4步  5步!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉不是美术社员也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…内卷你来告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是1853出生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,1890过世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他是荷兰的画家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,画家?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说暗号4的答案是梵高画过的向日葵的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有1幅烧毁了  但是一共有7幅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是7步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密宝物一定就在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  无论怎么努力  这里也不像是能挖的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么能挖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(710,660)}冈格尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,出现吧  永恒之枪!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:35.65,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：Gungnir  冈格尼尔  北欧神话中主神奥丁所使用的武器  是矮人族用世界之树的树枝打造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好短!  永恒之枪好短!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  凭我的魔力这就是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来就只有前端而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有写古文字吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没错没错  毕竟是永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,随便丢也能挖?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没错没错没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,行了别闹了  好了别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,体力劳动就交给就交给内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我来吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好像挖到什么坚硬的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,永恒之枪也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那我们就来进行开封仪式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,无论有什么  都由我们三等分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我不是美术社员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是我们三人找到的  这是当然的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们重要的冒险证明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,色情…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
